info.description:
Osirish Underground internet tool (based on osirish.co), Mainly for scanning your resource (cracking / bruteforce), you can install tool (plugin) for this application like:

* Dorker – Collecting url from major search engine.
* Sender – Smart email sender with proxy.
* and more Hacking or Spamming tool.

Support Platforms
-----------------

* Python 2 and Python 3
* win32, win_amd64, linux_i386, linux_x86_64, macosx_x86_64
* Embedded Platform: Raspberry Pi, Banana Pi, Orange Pi, TS-4600 / TS-7600

Quick Start
-----------

Install (choose one of command below)::

    pip install osirish
    python -m pip install osirish
    py -m pip install osirish

Run command (choose one of command below)::

    osirish
    python -m osirish
    py -m osirish
